10.10	Gosh%C5%ABsh%C5%8D-sama_Ninomiya-kun	Goshūshō-sama Ninomiya-kun	Goshūshō-sama Ninomiya-kun , Our Condolences, Ninomiya-kun) is a Japanese light novel series by Daisuke Suzuki, with illustrations by Kyourin Takanae. The light novel started serialization in Monthly Dragon Magazine in April 2005, published by Fujimi Shobo. A manga adaptation was being serialized in the shōnen manga magazine Monthly Dragon Age. An anime adaptation by AIC Spirits first aired in Japan on October 4, 2007.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/ed/Gosh%C5%ABsh%C5%8D-sama_Ninomiya-kun_logo.jpg/230px-Gosh%C5%ABsh%C5%8D-sama_Ninomiya-kun_logo.jpg
